  "texts": [
    "Many real life examples of ADM have, however, already proven the contrary, as Section III will show.",
    "The GDPR and the AI ACT both regulate ADM but with different scopes and types of protection.",
    "Article 22 GDPR contains a micro-charter for automated decisions to limit automated processes detrimental to human dignity and enhance the accountability and responsibility of human decision-makers.",
    "While generally prohibited, automated decisions that fulfill Article 22(2) conditions are exceptionally allowed, provided additional safeguards are present, including the right to contest the decision and obtain human intervention.",
    "Compared to the general provision on special categories of data (Article 9 GDPR), more stringent rules for processing sensitive data apply."
